mefloxacin, Ampicillin, Azithromycin, Ofloxacin, Ciprofloxacin, Famciclovir, Cefuroxime, Trifluridine, Moxifloxacin, More', 'Entrectinib, Imatinib, Pralsetinib, Dabrafenib, Asciminib, Acalabrutinib, Dacomitinib, Pexidartinib, Pacritinib, Tepotinib, Fedratinib, More', 1767369485);
